Replace the Coder Getting Started promo with a Composery welcome card

code-server injects a "Deploy code-server for your team" Coder advert into the
Welcome page (getting-started.diff). This swaps that block's contents for a
clean, theme-aware Composery card (icon, one line, link to docs.composery.io),
keeping the existing isEnabledCoderGettingStarted gate so it can still be turned
off with COMPOSERY_DISABLE_GETTING_STARTED_OVERRIDE.

